    "The proposed multi-task framework, which incorporates the hybrid architecture and CAF module, effectively integrates high-level and local information, leading to improved segmentation and classification results.",
    "This study contributes to advancing the field of medical image analysis by introducing a novel and efficient approach that outperforms existing methods in terms of both segmentation and classification.Fig. 11Fig.",
    "1 Flow chart of our contribution.",
    "(a) The proposed architecture to perform the segmentation of BUS images; (b) The proposed method to classify the segmented BUS images Fig. 22Fig.2The proposed architecture to perform the segmentation of BUS images FigureFigure 1b shows an overview of the classification of the segmented breast tumor regions extracted from the BUS images.",
    "Specifically, we leverage the strengths of the MLP-Mixer [18] model, which is a recently proposed architecture for image classification tasks, to achieve an accurate classification of BUS tumors."
